spgM3StripePushDown(25.10)                          spgM3StripePushDown(25.10)

Name
       spgM3StripePushDown

Syntax
       spgM3StripePushDown

       Specifies the width threshold in site units for virtual push down of M3
       stripe to M2 for M1 pin-access.

       If  the default value is set to -1, it indicates that no M3 stripe will
       be pushed down. If the default value is set to 0, it indicates that all
       M3 stripes will be pushed down. If the default value is larger than  0,
       then  all m3 stripes having width greater than the specified value will
       be pushed down.

